:$S \setminus \O \subseteq S$\nFrom the definition of [[Definition:Empty Set|the empty set]]:
:$\forall x \in S: x \notin \O$\nLet $x \in S$.\nThus:
{{begin-eqn}}
{{eqn | l = x \in S
